    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "apoo\nWe love to fly\nThe\nApollo\nFlyer\nPre-flight\nChecklist.\n1) Fold the Flyer in half,\nlongways, so the color is on\nthe inside.\n2) Now fold this triangular panel\ndown so its bottom edge lines up\nwith your first fold, and repeat on the\nother side.\n3) Fold this panel down again so its diag-\nonal edge lines up with your first fold, and\nrepeat on the other side.\n4) Now fold the new diagonal edge down so that\nit also lines up with your first fold, and repeat on\nthe other side.\n5) If your finished Flyer\nlooks like this, you're gonna\nlove to fly."
    ],
